Citation.sTitle: Measurement and Correlation of Solubility of Pimelic Acid in Ether, Tetrahydrofuran, Ethanol, and Methanol
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of pimelic acid in ether, tetrahydrofuran, ethanol, and methanol had been determined by the synthetic method. The experimental data were correlated with simplified Apelblat equation. The solubilities correlated by the model showed good agreement with experimental data.
